OL,3,CGovernment rejects call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into murder of Sean Brown
OL,6,FThe Secretary of State has insisted an
OL,7,Finquiry is not the best way to proceed
OL,8,F- instead encouraging the family to
OL,9,Fmeet with the Independent Commissioner
OL,10,Ffor Reconciliation and Information
OL,11,FRecovery.
OL,13,FMr Brown's family said they were
OL,14,F"devastated" at the decision but
OL,15,Fpledged that they would not be "going
OL,16,Faway".
OL,18,FEarlier this year, a coroner said an
OL,19,Finquest into Mr Brown's death could
OL,20,Fnot proceed due to the withholding of
OL,21,Fsensitive files.
