OL,6,FMr Justice Kinney said his ability to
OL,7,Fexamine Mr Brown's death had been
OL,8,F"compromised" by the extent of
OL,9,Fconfidential State material being
OL,10,Fexcluded from the proceedings on
OL,11,Fnational security grounds.
OL,13,FHe said he would write to the Northern
OL,14,FIreland Secretary to call on the
OL,15,FGovernment to establish a public
OL,16,Finquiry into the loyalist murder.
OL,18,FIn a statement on Friday, the family
OL,19,Fof Sean Brown said they had "waited
OL,20,Fpatiently" for a reply to that request.
