OL,3,CGovernment rejects call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into murder of Sean Brown
OL,6,F"We are today devastated that Hilary
OL,7,FBenn MP has acted in defiance of the
OL,8,Fjudiciary and has ignored the explicit
OL,9,Fdirection of a High Court judge to
OL,10,Fconvene a public inquiry.
OL,12,F"The State is terrified that their
OL,13,Fcarefully curated official history of
OL,14,Fthe conflict is now being contradicted
OL,15,Fby judicially endorsed legal facts,
OL,16,Fhence their attempts to deny victims
OL,17,Fof access to the courts and access to
OL,18,Fjustice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
