OL,3,CGovernment rejects call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into murder of Sean Brown
OL,6,F"Today's devastating decision is
OL,7,Fmerely an event in a long and shameful
OL,8,Fchronology, which must be an eternal
OL,9,Fembarrassment to the State.
OL,11,F"It is not the end of our journey; we
OL,12,Fare not going away.
OL,14,F"This is merely a decision which will
OL,15,Fbe challenged, and we will now look
OL,16,Fforward with renewed enthusiasm and
OL,17,Fvigour to our judicial review which
OL,18,Fwas already listed for hearing on
OL,19,FThursday 26 and Monday 30 September
OL,20,F2024.
