OL,3,CGovernment rejects call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into murder of Sean Brown
OL,6,FIn a statement, Mr Benn said he
OL,7,Fconcluded a public inquiry was "not
OL,8,Fthe best way to proceed".
OL,10,F"I have enormous sympathy for Mrs
OL,11,FBrown and her family, who have
OL,12,Fsuffered so much since the murder of
OL,13,Fher husband and their father," he said.
OL,15,F"I acknowledge their continued search
OL,16,Ffor answers in relation to this case
OL,17,Fand am grateful to them for meeting me
OL,18,Fon 28 August.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@XO]rD@AOUuD@^O]wD@AOU
