OL,3,CGovernment rejects call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into murder of Sean Brown
OL,6,F"I take my responsibility to victims
OL,7,Fand survivors of the Troubles
OL,8,Fextremely seriously.
OL,10,F"In reaching this decision, I
OL,11,Fcarefully considered a range of
OL,12,Ffactors, including the views of Mrs
OL,13,FBrown and her family, the coroner's
OL,14,Frulings, the Government's human rights
OL,15,Fobligations, and important public
OL,16,Finterest factors.
OL,18,F"Ultimately, I have concluded that an
OL,19,Finquiry under the Inquiries Act is not
OL,20,Fthe best way to proceed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUzD@AOU
