OL,6,F"I recognise that this decision will
OL,7,Fcome as a disappointment to the Brown
OL,8,Ffamily.
OL,10,F"I am, however, confident in the
OL,11,FIndependent Commissioner for
OL,12,FReconciliation and Information
OL,13,FRecovery's (ICRIR) capability to
OL,14,Fdeliver justice, accountability, and
OL,15,Finformation to victims and survivors
OL,16,Fof the Troubles, and to meet the
OL,17,FGovernment's human rights obligations,
OL,18,Fparticularly given the Northern
OL,19,FIreland High Court's ruling.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
