OL,6,F"I would therefore encourage Mrs Brown
OL,7,Fand her family to meet with Sir Declan
OL,8,F(Morgan) and the ICRIR to hear how the
OL,9,Findependent Commission would approach
OL,10,Fany investigation into Mr Brown's
OL,11,Fdeath."
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, Mr Benn announced that a
OL,14,Fpublic inquiry would be established
OL,15,Finto the murder of solicitor Pat
OL,16,FFinucane, who was shot dead in front
OL,17,Fof his family at their Belfast home in
OL,18,F1989.
