OL,6,FThe attack, carried out by the Ulster
OL,7,FDefence Association, was found by a
OL,8,Fseries of probes to have involved
OL,9,Fcollusion with the state.
OL,11,FMr Benn said he based the decision on
OL,12,Fthe "exceptional reason" that a UK
OL,13,Fgovernment had committed more than 20
OL,14,Fyears ago to hold an inquiry into Mr
OL,15,FFinucane's murder, which had remained
OL,16,F"unfulfilled".
